{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在n个人中，某些人的银行账号之间可以互相转账。这些人之间转账的手续费各不相同。给定这些人之间转账时需要从转账金额里扣除百分之几的手续费，请问A最少需要多少钱使得转账后B收到100元。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"最小花费 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出A使得B到账100元最少需要的总费用。精确到小数点后8位。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行输入两个正整数n,m，分别表示总人数和可以互相转账的人的对数。<p><p>以下m行每行输入三个正整数x,y,z，表示标号为x的人和标号为y的人之间互相转账需要扣除z%的手续费 (z<100)。<p><p>最后一行输入两个正整数A,B。数据保证A与B之间可以直接或间接地转账。<p>","examples":"<input>3 3\n1 2 1\n2 3 2\n1 3 3\n1 3\n</input><output>103.07153164\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"【数据规模】\n1≤n≤2000\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1344","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}